strings.Value: "We found greatbeast! Chief be very pleased!"
"Chief will reward us! Give us lots of grub!"
"Let's go to the village, lead chief to greatbeast!"

"Dumb rothead! Village be fa-a-a-r. From river be going towards sunrise, then be turning by moss-stone, then be stomp-stomping through hills long time! Going there and back again — pfft! -take too much time! Better we bring greatbeast to chief!"
"Yes, yes! Let it go there itself!"
"Hey! Greatbeast! Come on, get up, stomp-stomp! Now!"
"Hnh. What if greatbeast cannot hear us? Is it dead?"
{n}The owlbear is still slumbering. The goblins fidget and glance at each other.{/n}
"He not dead, he lazybones, don't want to go! Look, I show you."
"Hey!" {n}The goblin grabs a stick and pokes owlbear's beak with it.{/n} "You get up, lazybones! No sleep, come see chief!"
"Look! Greatbeast be awake! Be standing up! Be mighty greatbeast!"
"See it not dead, it awake now. Hey! No roaring! Put claws away, put-! HEY! US NO EAT! NO EAT! AAAAAA! MY LEGS!"
"Now greatbeast be listening to me! Behind us stomp-stomp! No noise! No roaring! You hear, lazybones? No roaring!"
